        "after": "<version>2.6.6</version>",
        "kind": "update_spring_boot_version",
        "bucket": "breaking"
      },
      {
        "general_idea": "Set the Java source and target version to 17.",
        "why_exists": "Without this change, the project compiles for Java 8, failing to utilize Java 17 features or potentially causing class version mismatches if mixed with Java 17 dependencies.",
